                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/1233" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-0167</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8808 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">泰达移动供电线缆有限公司的财税困局</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Taxation Dilemma of TaiDa Mobile Powered Cable Corporation</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">郑红霞，王颖等</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">华中科技大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">泰达移动供电线缆有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">能源工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">18 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">外商独资企业；税务风险；税收筹划；涉外税务；2013百优案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Wholly Foreign-owned Enterprise；Tax Risk；Tax Planning；International Taxation</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">外商投资企业在上世纪八、九十年代伴随着我国改革开放政策的实施而迅速发展，为中国积极有效地利用外资发展经济起到了重要作用。然而，经过这许多年的发展，外商投资企业，尤其是外商独资企业，因为外国母公司在管理上的鞭长莫及，加之涉外税务本身的复杂性，和我国近些年会计、税收方面改革频繁，其财税管理中的问题逐渐暴露。本案例选取在外商独资企业中具有代表性的泰达公司，分析其在税收管理中遇到的难题，特别针对外商投资企业特有的涉外税务事项探讨如何通过健全会计核算、加强内部控制、合理税收谋划以规避税务风险，减轻企业税负，从而帮助学生理解和掌握财务会计与税收的关系、税收筹划、税务风险管理以及外商投资企业特有的税务问题。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">In the eighties and nineties of last century, foreign-investment enterprises developed rapidly with the implementation of China&#39;s reform and opening-up policy, and also played an important role for China’s economic development. However, after these years of development, foreign-investment enterprises, especially wholly foreign-owned enterprises gradually exposed some problems in its accounting and taxation management, due to the plenty of management affairs are beyond the parent company&#39;s control, coupled with the complexity of international taxation, and frequently reformation of China&#39;s accounting and tax polices. The case studies representative corporation TaiDa in the wholly foreign-owned enterprises, and analyze tax problems which are often encountered in taxation management as well as specific foreign tax affairs to explore how to reduce tax burden and avoid the tax risk through strengthen accounting, internal control and tax planning. It could help students understand and master the correlations between accounting and tax, tax planning, tax risk management and specific tax problems in foreign-investment enterprises.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2011</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《税收理论与实务》、《税收筹划》、《税务会计》、《国际税收》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">健全会计核算、 加强内部控制、合理税收筹划</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2013-08</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
